[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/104] improved the alias expansion
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/100] created LICENSE
, added 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/99] Source command
, added 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/95] Variable completions and better ls
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/93] added unit parsing and eval support
, added 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/92] better completions for external args
, changed to 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/91] use list completions and better expansion
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/90] added path completions
, fixed so 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/87] lines shouldn't trim
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/86] added simple cd
, fixed to 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/83] let strings be cell paths
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/82] added select
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/81] added wrap and get and cell_path parsing
fdncred created 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/103] allow one to specify a custom separator for the grid
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/102] respect lscolors env var; measure width minus ansi
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/96] output 
``ls``
 as a grid vs table
xiuxiu62 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/101] added touch command
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/98] ported 
``cp``
 to fs commands
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/88] ported the mv command
stormasm created 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/97] The signature of the get command was mistakenly named wrap
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/85] added serde derive to Cargo.toml so nu-protocol compiles standalone
kubouch 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/89] added import patterns to 'hide'
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/74] Modules: export & hide
elferherrera created 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/84] prompt with env variable
